        "Q3 = df['AGE'].quantile(0.75)\n",

        "upper_bound = Q3 + 1.5 * IQR\n",
        "lower_bound = Q1 - 1.5 * IQR\n",
        "\n",
        "df = df[(df['AGE'] >= lower_bound) & (df['AGE'] <= upper_bound)]\n",
